      <title>随着能源价格下跌，欧洲铝产量开始复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/europe-s-aluminum-output-starts-to-recover-as-energy-prices-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Trimet Aluminium SE 将在明年将其位于法国和德国的冶炼厂的产量提高到满负荷，这表明能源价格下跌正在帮助欧洲铝工业从生存危机的边缘拉回来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/europe-s-aluminum-output-starts-to-recover-as-energy-prices-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 13:34:01 GMT</pubDate>
